opis: PRODAJA, KUĆA, ROVINJ, CENTAR, 156 M2 Prodajemo prekrasnu kuću u samom srcu Starog grada Rovinja veličine 156 m2. Kuća se sastoji od tri etaže te se svaka etaža koristi kao studio apartman. Svaki apartman ima vlastiti ulaz i potpuno su opremljeni, kategorizirani i etažirani. Kuća je kompletno adaptirana prije 18 godina.  Kuća je od rive udaljena 60 metara. Vlasništvo uredno. Cijena 675.000 Eura FOR SALE, HOUSE, ROVINJ, CENTER, 156 M2 We are selling a beautiful house in the heart of the Old Town of Rovinj, measuring 156 m2. The house consists of three floors and each floor is used as a studio apartment. Each apartment has its own entrance and is fully equipped and categorized. The house was completely renovated 18 years ago. The house is only 60 meters from the sea.
